# CRM Campaign Analysis
Portfolio project focused on CRM, SQL, customer journey analysis and AI automation.

# CRM Campaign Analysis

## 📌 Project Overview

This project simulates the work of a CRM Analyst for a food delivery company.

The objective is to analyze customer behavior, identify opportunities to improve retention, and propose CRM strategies supported by SQL, dashboards, and AI-powered automation.

---

## 🎯 Business Problem

Only 18% of new users complete their first purchase after installing the app.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

- Analyze customer behavior using SQL
- Measure CRM KPIs
- Design customer journeys
- Build a Power BI dashboard
- Propose AI-powered automation ideas

---

## 🛠️ Tools

- SQL
- Power BI
- Excel
- GitHub
- ChatGPT

---

## 📈 KPIs

- DAU
- Conversion Rate
- Retention Rate
- ARPDAU
- LTV

---

## 🚧 Project Status

Work in progress...
